com.adobe.livecycle.rightsmanagement.client.infomodel
Class EventSearchFilter

java.lang.Object
  com.adobe.livecycle.rightsmanagement.client.infomodel.EventSearchFilter

public class EventSearchFilter
extends java.lang.Object

Enables you to define search criteria that are used while searching for events. You pass this object to the searchForEvents method. To see an object of this type used in a code example, see the Searching for events using the Java API quick start in Programming with Adobe Experience Manager Forms.
